text: Ang Thong Province Stadium () is a multi-purpose stadium in Ang Thong Province, Thailand. It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of Angthong F.C.. The stadium holds 6,000 people.https://en.klaiklai.com/places/THPOI38136404/ang-thong- stadiumhttp://www.siamsport.co.th/column/detail/32665 ==References== Category:Football venues in Thailand Category:Multi-purpose stadiums in Thailand Category:Angthong F.C.
